@page "/about"
<div>
    <h1>About</h1><hr>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Where to begin: </strong><a href="https://slowly.app/en/">SLOWLY app</a></li>
        <li>
            This website helps you collect Slowly stamps and compare your collection with your penpals.
        </li>

    </ul>
</div>
<div>
    <h3>Features</h3><hr>
    <ul>
        <li>A table of all SLOWLY stamps with details: price, region, group, name, description, and rarity.</li>
        <li>A table of the number of different language speakers on Slowly.</li>
        <li>Stamp image in the table is 100 x 100 pixels.</li>
        <li>Click the image to display an enlarged stamp with the background image.</li>
        <li>Search box (WIP)</li>
    </ul>
</div>
